Sorting data in a particular manner:
Syntax: Select column name from table order y column name;
select author_name from books order by price;
---------------------------------------------------------------------
select title, pages from books order by pages desc limit 1;
select title, pages from books order by pages limit 0,2
-----------------------------------------------------------------
Most Recent 3 eneteries:

select concat(title,'-',released_year) as Summary from books order by released_year desc limit 3;
